# Web Scraper with Telegram Notifications

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.x-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/yourusername/web-scraper)
![Contributions welcome](https://img.shields.io/badge/contributions-welcome-brightgreen)

This Python application scrapes content from a website, stores it in a PostgreSQL database, and sends notifications to a Telegram channel about new content.

---

